# ---- .NET (backend) ----
bin/
obj/
# NOTE: do NOT add unanchored `[Dd]ebug/` / `[Rr]elease/` here. .NET build output already lives under
# bin/ + obj/ (covered above); an unanchored debug/release dir pattern also silently swallows SOURCE
# directories like android/app/src/debug/ (S7: the whole Android debug source set went uncommitted this
# way, absent on CI). If a non-standard .NET output dir ever appears, anchor it (e.g. backend/**/bin/).
*.user
project.lock.json
.vs/
TestResults/

