# ---- Font Awesome PRO (LICENSED, PAID — never in a public repo) ----
# FA's Pro license explicitly forbids committing Pro files to a public repository. This repo is public,
# so every FA Pro binary is hard-ignored here regardless of where it is placed in the tree. The glyph→
# codepoint MAPPING (design/fa-glyph-map.json) is data, not a font, and IS committed. See the pointer
# pointer docs ios/DesignKit/FONTS.md and android/designkit/FONTS.md for how the licensed .otf files get
# placed locally (ios/DesignKit/Fonts/, android/designkit/src/main/assets/fonts/) / injected into a
# build. Matched by NAME so the
# ignore holds no matter the directory. M PLUS Rounded 1c (OFL) is NOT matched — it is freely
# redistributable and its own asset-drop task.
**/FontAwesome*.otf
**/fontawesome*.otf
**/Font Awesome*.otf

# ---- Infra ----
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
.terraform/
